LANE CLOSURE INFO: Starting on February 18 2019 motorists can expect lane closures on Route 8 between I-95 in Bridgeport and Exit 14 in Shelton. Traffic control personnel and signing patterns will be utilized to guide motorists through the work zone. The regular work schedules for this project is 9:00 a.m. to 3:00 p.m. and 9:00 p.m. to 5:00 a.m. (Monday through Friday). Segments of the following routes will be impacted by this project:-I-95 in the vicinity of Exit 27 (Bridgeport)-Route 1 at the Route 8 interchange (Bridgeport)-Route 8 (Bridgeport Trumbull and Shelton)-Route 15 at the Route 8 Interchange (Trumbull)-Route 108 at the Route 8 interchange (Bridgeport)-Route 110/Howe Ave at the Route 8 Interchange (Shelton)-	Route 714/Bridgeport Ave at the Route 8 Interchange (Shelton)Motorists should be aware that modifications or extensions to this schedule may become necessary due to weather delays or other unforeseen conditions. Motorists are urged to obey the posted speed
